				\begin{document}$$q_{\mathrm{sp}} = p \times q_{\mathrm{e}}$$\end{document}). The ratio of ion to electron charge is always qi/qe=-1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
